dct_description_sm: Abstract: Map of Port Royal, Jamaica, showing streets, forts, and selected buildings, prior to the earthquake of June 7, 1692.
Notes: Oriented with north to the upper right.
Likely detached from November 1785 issue of Gentleman's magazine.
Publisher information from online digital scan of November 1785 issue of Gentleman's magazine.
Includes illustration of a column topped with a statue of a seated woman.
